Gallery Store, which dissolves into a gallery. CARLOS CHAVEZ / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Works such as these tin men and skeleton scene, at left, can be 
purchased. JOAN M. ZOPF-PAHOYO / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
