BARRIOS; GUERRILLAS -- NICARAGUA; SEMIAUTOMATIC WEAPONS; MILITARY FORCE 
REDUCTIONS; NICARAGUA -- SECURITY; UNITED NICARAGUAN OPPOSITION; SANDINISTA 
NATIONAL LIBERATION FRONT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
