<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE DEATH OF HANK GATHERS; 
</P>
<P>
GATHERS TOUCHED THOSE WHO KNEW HIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I enjoy the writings of Mike Downey and often find his work very humorous. 
</P>
<P>
On Monday, I was deeply moved by Mike's piece and found it difficult to finish 
reading it. 
</P>
<P>
My younger brother, Paul, a student at Santa Clara University, was so amazed by 
Hank Gathers' performances that he nicknamed him "F-Gathers," as in an F-4 
fighter jet. I used to like that nickname, but we'll use it no more. Our 
fighter has been shot down. 
</P>
<P>
We will all miss Hank the basketball player, but mostly we will miss Hank the 
person. 
</P>
<P>
BILL KOMAR 
</P>
<P>
Playa del Rey 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
