<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Balancing Act Chinese peasant carries goods and child on either end of 
yoke as he crosses a street near Beijing's Tian An Men Square today. MARK AVERY 
/ Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
