<P>
MAIN STORY 
</P>
<P>
MGM/UA agrees to be bought by Pathe Communications Corp., the European film 
conglomerate. A1 
</P>
<P>
ANALYSIS 
</P>
<P>
Times Film Editor Jack Mathews takes a look at what Pathe is getting for its 
$1-billion investment. F1 
</P>
<P>
CHRONOLOGY 
</P>
<P>
A month-by-month look at how MGM went down the Yellow Brick Road of high 
finance with Las Vegas entrepreneur Kirk Kerkorian. D8 
</P>
